pullWithRsync

public final boolean pullWithRsync(java.lang.String remoteName,
                                   java.io.File localFile)
Execute "rsync -Laz ". If necessary, the directories leading to the local file will be created. This will wait and retry a number of times if the rsync fails unless the failure is because of the remote file not existing.

Parameters:
remoteName - of the form machine:path
localFile - path to local destination.
